---
title: Upload → Moderation → Public Library flow
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> uploading: User selects PDF/EPUB

    uploading --> ingesting: PUT to S3 succeeds<br/>(< 50MB, content-type OK)

    state ingesting {
        [*] --> hashing
        hashing --> clamav_scan: SHA-256 computed
        clamav_scan --> extract_meta: clean
        clamav_scan --> rejected_clamav: infected
        extract_meta --> render_cover: title, author, page_count
        render_cover --> [*]
    }

    ingesting --> private: Book row ready (default visibility)
    ingesting --> rejected_clamav: virus detected
    rejected_clamav --> [*]: file deleted from S3

    private --> pending_review: Owner toggles "Make Public"
    pending_review --> public: Moderator approves
    pending_review --> rejected_mod: Moderator rejects (with reason)
    pending_review --> private: Moderator requests edits

    public --> private: Owner toggles back
    public --> rejected_takedown: 3+ reports OR DMCA takedown
    public --> [*]: Owner deletes (soft-delete)

    rejected_mod --> private: Owner edits + re-submits
    rejected_takedown --> [*]
